<TD WIDTH=380 ALIGN=LEFT><FONT SIZE=2>
<STRONG>Where:</STRONG>&nbsp;&nbsp;Mt. McKinley, Denali, Alaska, USA (20,320 ft)<BR>
<BR>
<STRONG>What:</STRONG>&nbsp;&nbsp;Multi-terrain/Glacier climbing<BR>
<BR>
<STRONG>When:</STRONG>&nbsp;&nbsp;<%=date+7%> - <%=date+21%> (14 days)<BR>
<BR>
<STRONG>Who:</STRONG>&nbsp;&nbsp;Adaptable, moderately experienced 
climbers with high level of endurance<BR>
<BR>
<STRONG>How:</STRONG>&nbsp;&nbsp;10-12 climbers with 2 instructors<BR>
<BR>
<STRONG>Cost:</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;$2,700 AW member, $3,200 nonmember<BR>
<BR>
</TD>
